improved_metadata.title: Clipper Chaos: The Barber Prank Anthem
improved_metadata.description: This song is about a viral prank war between two barbers, Kyro and Robert, escalating into comical haircut fails and roaring laughter. The track captures the chaotic energy of their barber shop battles and the absurdity of their pranks.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Clipper chaos ain't no stopping Roberts, Pranks got the whole room popping
